products.title: William Morris Sunflower Silver Grey Roller Blind
products.description: From their william morris range in collaboration with v&a, the sunflower design was originally produced in 1879 and is still on trend today. The soft greys make this design versatile, allowing it to harmonise perfectly with a range of colours and styles of homes.
